description:
Minecraft modded. Team Canada is back together again in Sky Factory 2.5. This is a custom mod pack by Bacon Donut where the goal is to build your world while starting out with basically nothing.

This mod pack is available from the FTB launcher:
http://www.feed-the-beast.com/
